messages.message:
23.04 code cut :scissors:
friendly reminder that our next major release *`23.04 code cut will happen next Monday 4/3`* around noon PST, _*`we will take the latest successful dogfood deployment for code cut`*_ which means *`you should make sure to get your code in earlier so it can be part of the dogfood build`*.

23.04 UAT :test_tube:
also to prepare the UAT test we've created the 23.04 UAT test on testmo and duplicated the test assignment as 23.02 UAT, you no longer have to find the tests and change the assignment if you will be working on the same set of tests, it should show up under the `my work` tab on testmo.
for the team leads please take a look and make adjustment of the test cases if they are different than 23.02, thanks :pray:

For UAT tests in Testmo, questions that came up during 23.02 UAT are compiled under this page. Hope this helps :pray:
https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RELENG/pages/2003599387/UAT+with+Testmo+FAQs
